      <a href="#"><h3>Where will the visualization be hosted?</h3></a>
      <p>All our maps are hosted on CartoDB dedicated MaaS instances. If you already licence a dedicated CartoDB instance, you will have the option of hosting your dataset on your own account.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="#"><h3>I want to use a different set of tiles for the base layer. Is it possible?</h3></a>
      <p>Yes, we are able to use Google Maps, Bing, MapBox, Open Street Maps, or your own base map tiles.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="#"><h3>Which browsers do your maps support?</h3></a>
      <p>Our maps work out of the box on all modern browsers this includes, Google Chrome 12+, Internet Explorer 9,+ Firefox 4+, Safari 5+, Opera 9+, including most mobile browsers on iOS and Android, </p>
    </li>    
